text: National Highway 373, commonly referred to as NH 373 is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 73. NH-373 runs in the state of Karnataka in India. == Route == NH373 connects Belur, Hassan, Holenarasipura and Bilikere in the state of Karnataka. == Junctions == : Terminal near Belur. : near Hassan : Terminal near Bilikere. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 373 on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Karnataka
